artistic labels, minimalist ceramics, and neatly packaged bags of specialty coffee, all arranged with just the right amount of space to let each piece breathe.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-10.jpg 1453w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-10-940x1242.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-10-800x1057.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-10-768x1015.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-10-1162x1536.jpg 1162w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1453px) 100vw, 1453px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eSeating throughout the café is designed to foster both solitude and connection. Built-in benches follow the clean architectural lines, while custom-made tables and stools echo the same material clarity. Nothing feels off-the-shelf, every piece of furniture has been created specifically for this project, reinforcing the sense of calm, continuity, and care. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1780\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-11.jpg\" alt=\"Seating throughout the café is designed to foster both solitude and connection. Built-in benches follow the clean architectural lines, while custom-made tables and stools echo the same material clarity. Nothing feels off-the-shelf, every piece of furniture has been created specifically for this project, reinforcing the sense of calm, continuity, and care. \" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-11.jpg 1780w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-11-940x1014.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-11-800x863.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-11-768x828.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-11-1424x1536.jpg 1424w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1780px) 100vw, 1780px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe placement of seating reflects a philosophy of flow: there’s breathing room between tables, yet intimacy is still possible. Whether you’re perched at the window bench with a morning espresso or seated deeper inside with a glass of natural wine, the experience is the same, unhurried, deliberate, and rooted in comfort.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1766\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-12.jpg\" alt=\"Seating throughout the café is designed to foster both solitude and connection. Built-in benches follow the clean architectural lines, while custom-made tables and stools echo the same material clarity. Nothing feels off-the-shelf, every piece of furniture has been created specifically for this project, reinforcing the sense of calm, continuity, and care. \" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-12.jpg 1766w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-12-940x1022.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-12-800x870.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-12-768x835.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-12-1413x1536.jpg 1413w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1766px) 100vw, 1766px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eLighting plays a quiet but critical role. Natural light is the primary element, flooding the space through those expansive folding windows during the day. The pine panels and ceramic surfaces respond beautifully to this shifting light, deepening in tone as the day moves on. As evening falls, the atmosphere shifts subtly. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1814\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-13.jpg\" alt=\"Seating throughout the café is designed to foster both solitude and connection. Built-in benches follow the clean architectural lines, while custom-made tables and stools echo the same material clarity. Nothing feels off-the-shelf, every piece of furniture has been created specifically for this project, reinforcing the sense of calm, continuity, and care. \" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-13.jpg 1814w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-13-940x995.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-13-800x847.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-13-768x813.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-13-1451x1536.jpg 1451w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1814px) 100vw, 1814px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eDiscreet, well-placed hidden lighting picks up where the sun leaves off, emphasizing texture rather than brightness. There’s no harshness, no overhead glare, just soft, ambient light that reflects the café’s ethos of calm clarity.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1892\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-14.jpg\" alt=\"Discreet, well-placed hidden lighting in this cafe picks up where the sun leaves off, emphasizing texture rather than brightness. There’s no harshness, no overhead glare, just soft, ambient light that reflects the café’s ethos of calm clarity.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-14.jpg 1892w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-14-940x954.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-14-800x812.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-14-768x779.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-14-1514x1536.jpg 1514w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1892px) 100vw, 1892px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eEven the restroom in this café carries the same refined calm as the rest of the space. Tucked behind a dark-stained wooden door, it opens to a minimalist, softly lit interior where every detail feels considered. Warm wood cabinetry lies beneath a corner mirror trimmed with a halo of indirect lighting that casts a gentle glow across the room.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1674\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-15.jpg\" alt=\"Even the restroom in this café carries the same refined calm as the rest of the space. Tucked behind a dark-stained wooden door, it opens to a minimalist, softly lit interior where every detail feels considered. Warm wood cabinetry lies beneath a corner mirror trimmed with a halo of indirect lighting that casts a gentle glow across the room.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-15.jpg 1674w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-15-940x1078.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-15-800x918.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-15-768x881.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-15-1339x1536.jpg 1339w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1674px) 100vw, 1674px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1836\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-16.jpg\" alt=\"Even the restroom in this café carries the same refined calm as the rest of the space. Tucked behind a dark-stained wooden door, it opens to a minimalist, softly lit interior where every detail feels considered. Warm wood cabinetry lies beneath a corner mirror trimmed with a halo of indirect lighting that casts a gentle glow across the room.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-16.jpg 1836w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-16-940x983.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-16-800x837.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-16-768x803.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-16-1469x1536.jpg 1469w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1836px) 100vw, 1836px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eHere’s a glimpse into the design vision, captured in a single sketch.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1219\" height=\"891\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-17.jpg\" alt=\"A glimpse into the designer’s vision, captured in a single sketch.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-17.jpg 1219w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-17-940x687.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-17-800x585.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-cafe-coffee-shop-interior-design-060625-1211-17-768x561.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1219px) 100vw, 1219px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn OFF LINE, Ramón Esteve Estudio has built more than a coffee shop. They’ve created a setting for presence, a moment of stillness, tucked into the city’s most historic streets.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://www.alfonsocalza.com/\"\u003eAlfonso Calza\u003c/a\u003e | Studio: Ramón Esteve Estudio (Architect: Ramón Esteve, Project Team: Marisa Ridaura) | Building engineer: Sergio Cremades | Image: Tudi Soriano | Constructor: Construcciones Francés\u003c/h6\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
